Description
--------------------------------------------------

%{RELEASE} is a powerful memory optimization utility designed to help you get
the most out of your system's RAM. It monitors memory usage in real-time and
allows you to quickly free up memory by clearing the working sets of all
running processes.

Key Features:
- Real-time memory and page file monitoring with visual graphs
- One-click memory optimization button
- Process working set clearing for all running processes
- Automatic memory reduction when thresholds are exceeded
- Modern dark-themed user interface with live statistics
- Multi-language support (English, Korean)
- Customizable optimization settings and priority controls
- Optimization count tracking

--------------------------------------------------
Installing
--------------------------------------------------

Run the installer and follow the on-screen instructions. Administrative rights
are recommended for optimal performance when clearing process working sets.

--------------------------------------------------
Portable
--------------------------------------------------

For portable operation, select "Portable" during installation. All settings
will be stored in the application directory rather than AppData, making it
easy to run from a USB drive or cloud storage.

